      			<lb n="5" break="no"/>toḻilar pērāṟ paṅkaḷa-nāṭ-uṭaiyār-<unclear reason="eccentric_ductus">c= cū</unclear>
      			<lb n="6" break="no"/>ḷ<unclear reason="eccentric_ductus">ai</unclear>kaḷ ciṟiya-naṅk<choice><sic>e</sic><corr>ai</corr></choice>yār ceyvitta <hi rend="grantha">śrī</hi>-kōyil
